seller_notes: Call 512-900-6192 today to learn more about this exceptional 2023 Chevrolet Express 2500 LS, available at Covert Chrysler Dodge Jeep Ram Bee Cave in Bee Cave, Texas. This Summit White passenger van is designed to meet all your transportation needs with its powerful performance, spacious interior, and advanced safety features. Act now to take advantage of our free delivery anywhere in Texas.  Unmatched Performance  The 2023 Chevrolet Express 2500 LS is equipped with a robust engine and a 3.42 rear axle ratio, ensuring optimal power and efficiency for both city driving and highway cruising. The heavy-duty rear locking differential enhances traction and stability, making it ideal for various driving conditions. The front-wheel independent suspension system provides a smooth and comfortable ride, while the 4-wheel disc brakes and ABS ensure reliable stopping power.  Premium Features and Options  This Express 2500 LS comes with the Preferred Equipment Group 1LS, offering a range of amenities designed for comfort and convenience. The 12-passenger seating configuration (2-3-3-4) provides ample space for passengers, with a 4th-row bench seat adding to its versatility. The Driver Convenience Package includes cruise control and a tilt-wheel steering column for enhanced driving comfort. Stay connected with Bluetooth for phone, and enjoy your favorite music on the AM/FM Stereo with MP3 player. The custom vinyl seat trim ensures durability, while power windows, power door mirrors, and air conditioning enhance the overall driving experience. Additional features include a leather-wrapped steering wheel, steering wheel-mounted audio controls, and a deluxe console with swing-out storage bin for added convenience.  Safety and Driver Assistance  Safety is a top priority in the 2023 Chevrolet Express 2500 LS. It is equipped with dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, and an overhead airbag system to protect all occupants. The Electronic Stability Control and traction control systems provide enhanced handling and stability, while the rear park assist feature aids in maneuvering the van in tight spaces. The passenger cancellable airbag offers flexibility depending on seating arrangements. Additional safety features include a low tire pressure warning system, fully automatic headlights, and variably intermittent wipers.  Experience Excellence at Covert Chrysler Dodge Jeep Ram Bee Cave  At Covert Chrysler Dodge Jeep Ram Bee Cave, we are committed to providing top-quality vehicles and exceptional customer service. Whether you're in Bee Cave, Austin, or anywhere in Texas, we offer free delivery to make your purchase as convenient as possible. Our team is ready to assist you with flexible financing options and answer any questions you may have about this outstanding 2023 Chevrolet Express 2500 LS. Call 512-900-6192 today to schedule a test drive or arrange delivery. Don't miss out on this versatile and capable passenger van—contact us now before it's gone!

seller_notes: Call 512-900-6192 today to learn more about this exceptional 2023 Chevrolet Express 2500 LS, available at Covert Chrysler Dodge Jeep Ram Bee Cave in Bee Cave, Texas. This Summit White passenger van is designed to meet all your transportation needs with its powerful performance, spacious interior, and advanced safety features. Act now to take advantage of our free delivery anywhere in Texas.  Unmatched Performance  The 2023 Chevrolet Express 2500 LS is equipped with a robust engine and a 3.42 rear axle ratio, ensuring optimal power and efficiency for both city driving and highway cruising. The heavy-duty rear locking differential enhances traction and stability, making it ideal for various driving conditions. The front-wheel independent suspension system provides a smooth and comfortable ride, while the 4-wheel disc brakes and ABS ensure reliable stopping power.  Premium Features and Options  This Express 2500 LS comes with the Preferred Equipment Group 1LS, offering a range of amenities designed for comfort and convenience. The 12-passenger seating configuration (2-3-3-4) provides ample space for passengers, with a 4th-row bench seat adding to its versatility. The Driver Convenience Package includes cruise control and a tilt-wheel steering column for enhanced driving comfort. Stay connected with Bluetooth for phone, and enjoy your favorite music on the AM/FM Stereo with MP3 player. The custom vinyl seat trim ensures durability, while power windows, power door mirrors, and air conditioning enhance the overall driving experience. Additional features include a leather-wrapped steering wheel, steering wheel-mounted audio controls, and a deluxe console with swing-out storage bin for added convenience.  Safety and Driver Assistance  Safety is a top priority in the 2023 Chevrolet Express 2500 LS. It is equipped with dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, and an overhead airbag system to protect all occupants. The Electronic Stability Control and traction control systems provide enhanced handling and stability, while the rear park assist feature aids in maneuvering the van in tight spaces. The passenger cancellable airbag offers flexibility depending on seating arrangements. Additional safety features include a low tire pressure warning system, fully automatic headlights, and variably intermittent wipers.  Experience Excellence at Covert Chrysler Dodge Jeep Ram Bee Cave  At Covert Chrysler Dodge Jeep Ram Bee Cave, we are committed to providing top-quality vehicles and exceptional customer service. Whether you're in Bee Cave, Austin, or anywhere in Texas, we offer free delivery to make your purchase as convenient as possible. Our team is ready to assist you with flexible financing options and answer any questions you may have about this outstanding 2023 Chevrolet Express 2500 LS. Call 512-900-6192 today to schedule a test drive or arrange delivery. Don't miss out on this versatile and capable passenger van—contact us now before it's gone!
